{"about_the_game":"The latest title in the RIDGE RACER franchise, RIDGE RACER Unbounded gears up to carve its own destructive path with a new breed of arcade racing.<br><br>RIDGE RACER Unbounded brings an unexpected dimension to the series, delivering an original blast of ferocious racing adrenaline. Join the Unbounded street racing gang, lead by Kara Shindo, and test your driving skills against rivals in every street and alley of Shatter Bay. Prove your worth, get respect and expand your turf.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\"> Key Features</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Crash through everything - Cutting edge physics and effects combine to bring direct destruction like you\u2019ve never seen before. Unleash your rage to obliterate everything in your way and carve your own path.<br></li><li>Race in urban environments - Shatter Bay lives by its own rules and is ripe for being torn apart by the overpowered vehicles rampaging through its many areas, including the commercial zone, refinery, port, and high-rise construction site.<br></li><li>New breed of racing machines - Traditional racing machines are out and dozens of badass street machines are in, including the legendary RIDGE RACER Angel and Devil cars.</li></ul>","achievements":{"highlighted":[{"name":"Learning the ropes","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/202310/2c32c922252d744708bfacb97677e76b3adcb2b7.jpg"},{"name":"Champion","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/202310/6d064f18a3551ea4ff526fbaa7c962ec849cdd1b.jpg"},{"name":"Race Dominator","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/202310/5b9298ef8e78f5271866547b82a4ad1663ece800.jpg"},{"name":"Winning!","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/202310/c86d0034d6b15626ff9666dd707da80420175635.jpg"},{"name":"High Flyer","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/202310/7e93d202b5ed48308e73075f351380